         <abstract id="aspace_383e44980a46079d5d0a8f64813e152a">Collection of medium format mounted black and white and color reproductions of Pre-Columbian architecture, ceramics, paintings, sculpture and applied and decorative arts. Content varies from original photographic prints to reproductions from magazines and other published sources. Some sections have accompanying clippings folders.</abstract>
