      <scopecontent id="aspace_sc">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Collection of medium format mounted black and white and color reproductions of Pre-Columbian architecture, ceramics, paintings, sculpture and applied and decorative arts. Content varies from original photographic prints to reproductions from magazines and other published sources. Some sections have accompanying clippings folders.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
